Welcome to Nectar’s Water Quality Sensor documentation!¶

The Nectar Water Quality Sensor platform provides tools for testing the quality of water for botanical systems. We implement open source software such as TI-RTOS, and InfluxDB for a reliable and cutting edge approach.
